==Literature==

===Articles===

* Han Qi 韩琦: F. Furtado (1578-1653) S.J. and his Chinese translation of Aristotle’s ’Cosmology’. In: História das ciências matemáticas: Portugal e o Oriente, pp. 169-179 [[@http://www1.ihns.ac.cn/members/hanqi/pdf.databank/2-21.pdf|pdf]] 
* Corsi Ambrosetti, Elisabetta 伊丽 (Yi Li): From the Aristoteles latinus to the Aristoteles sinicus: Fragments of an unfinished project. In: Light a candle: Encounters and friendship with China: Festschrift in honour of Angelo Lazzarotto P.I.M.E., pp. 115-130
* Isabelle Duceux: El Aristoteles Sinicus: Examen del comentario aristotélico en chino de la primera Edad Moderna desde una perspectiva comparativa. relaciones 131 (2012), pp. 19-42. [[@http://www.colmich.edu.mx/files/relaciones/131/pdf/Duceux.pdf|pdf]] 
* Meynard, Thierry 梅谦立 (Mei Qianli): Aristotelian ethics in the land of Confucius: A study of Vagnone’s ’Western learning on personal cultivation’. Antiquorum philosophia 7 (2013), pp. 145-169